    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192750/extras/6d8da1d12ba7a4b30dda3b8d0f92a2eb.avif?t=1743967285\" width=225 height=120 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Ankhway</strong>  it's a 2D Indie <i>Adventure</i> and <i>Sci-fi</i> videogame with an epic, original and intriguing story that incorporates systems like jumping to avoid traps such as spikes, shooting, ''MP3 Player'' Item to listen to the soundtrack completely free in-game... Among many other mechanics and game systems! Combining the adventure (Exploration, puzzle-solving etc) with action and science fiction.</h2><br><br><strong><u>NEO-RETRO MODERN PIXEL ART STYLE GRAPHICS</u></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features gorgeous, colorful hand-drawn pixel art by awesome artists like <i>Rinober</i>, <i>KR</i> or <i>NeonPixel</i></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192750/extras/35Short1.gif?t=1743967285\" /></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192750/extras/07f079424c14e672a19d1fd92632135a.avif?t=1743967285\" width=280 height=80 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In a remote and wild area of the Sahara Desert <br>an adventurer expert in Hieroglyphs and history<br>of Egypt has just discovered something that would <br>change many more things you could never think about.<br><br><br>After days of working to dig everything up, he discovers<br>what turns out to be some underground ruins, a small<br>pyramid and a sphinx in perfect condition, thus revealing its<br>face. In addition, a strange opening but in the ground, so the pyramid<br>seems inaccessible and it seems like it acts as an antenna,<br>is located at the top of what appears to be<br>the entrance to some secret passages.<br><br><br>The Egyptian government seems astonished but nervous and<br>scared, they somehow know that the adventurous explorer<br>is going to get into the underground ruins to explore <br>this unknown place.<br><br><br><br>After arduous discussions, he managed to get them to leave him, <br>however, they feel responsible for what may happen to him and <br>they will wait at the exit.<br><br><br><br>This can certainly be the beginning of his great adventure\\..\\..\\..</h2><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192750/extras/c1fc1efe1f22b0e59f33a8058fcb93ce.avif?t=1743967285\" width=280 height=80 /></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><i><strong><u>Real Time Action</u></strong></i></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192750/extras/cb81e01951be1f729759cca35772a361.poster.avif?t=1743967285\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192750/extras/cb81e01951be1f729759cca35772a361.webm?t=1743967285\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192750/extras/cb81e01951be1f729759cca35772a361.mp4?t=1743967285\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><i><strong><u>Melee Weapons</u></strong></i></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192750/extras/54d7ef39357e9428aae2b698a5797c3f.poster.avif?t=1743967285\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192750/extras/54d7ef39357e9428aae2b698a5797c3f.webm?t=1743967285\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/app